                        <interp inst="t18720226-name-37" type="given" value="JESSIE"></interp>JESSIE HORNBY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Stephen Hornby, of Charles Street, Mid<lb></lb>dlesex Hospital—on 15th January I received a counterfeit florin from Miss Whitmore, and saw the prisoner in the shop—on the 6th, the Saturday week previous, I took a bad half-crown out of the glass, and broke it.</p>
